Problem: I stopped using YellowPages and moved onto WhitePages... but the page they gave me is all blank!

File: [THE_FILE](https://github.com/Yorzaren/ctf/raw/master/picoCTF-2019/problem-files/whitepages.txt "Download file")

Solution: Opening the file you see all the text file is just spaces. But opening it in notepad++ you see squares and \* which tells you there's more than one type of space being used. Replacing the spaces with 1 and 0, you can translate it into text.

![no-alignment]({{ '/picoCTF-2019/solution-files/whitepages.jpg' | absolute_url }})

```

```

Translated from binary to text.

```

		picoCTF

		SEE PUBLIC RECORDS & BACKGROUND REPORT
		5000 Forbes Ave, Pittsburgh, PA 15213
		picoCTF{not_all_spaces_are_created_equal_c167040c738e8bcae2109ef4be5960b1}
		
```

Flag: ```picoCTF{not_all_spaces_are_created_equal_c167040c738e8bcae2109ef4be5960b1}```
